Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:02.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi chiamo Shinichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Fino a poco tempo fa,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ero un famoso detective liceale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:07.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma una misteriosa organizzazione
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:09.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,mi ha trasformato in Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Non importa se sono piccolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho il cervello di un grande detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Qualunque sia il caso,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:15.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,la verità è sempre una sola!
