Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Piace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certo che no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non farti un'idea sbagliata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Davvero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allora continuo da solo...
