Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspetta, Tomoya Ogino...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Dove ho già sentito questo nome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eccolo qui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoya Ogino, cinque anni.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,È morto dopo essere stato operato da Ogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tre anni fa, il diciannove febbraio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:26.84,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFF7&\3c&H3D3D3D&\an7\blur1\bord1.2\shad0\fscx100\fscy100\pos(90,63.5)\p1\fad(500,200)}m -16 -60 l 338 -60 338 8 -16 8
